---
import BaseLayout from "../layouts/BaseLayout.astro";
---

<BaseLayout
  title="About | Taylor Heathcote"
  description="A visual profile for Taylor Heathcote — game design graduate, QA-minded creative, and detail-focused generalist."
  currentPage="about"
>
  <section class="about-sheet">
    <div class="about-sheet-grid">
      <section class="panel about-card about-profile-card">
        <p class="sheet-label">Profile Sheet</p>

        <h1>Taylor Heathcote</h1>

        <p class="about-role">
          Creative generalist with a background in game design, QA testing,
          digital media, and thoughtful presentation.
        </p>

        <p class="about-summary">
          I’m interested in work that feels intentional — visually,
          structurally, and emotionally. My strengths sit around creative
          problem-solving, design communication, player-facing thinking, and the
          kind of polish that helps a project feel coherent rather than patched
          together.
        </p>

        <div class="about-tag-list">
          <span class="about-tag">Game Design</span>
          <span class="about-tag">QA Testing</span>
          <span class="about-tag">UI / UX Design</span>
          <span class="about-tag">Creative Problem-Solving</span>
          <span class="about-tag">Detail-Focused</span>
        </div>

        <div class="about-specialisms">
          <p class="about-subsection-label">Specialisms</p>

          <div class="about-specialism-list">
            <span class="about-specialism">Game Design</span>
            <span class="about-specialism">QA Testing</span>
            <span class="about-specialism">UI / UX Design</span>
            <span class="about-specialism">Design Documentation</span>
            <span class="about-specialism">Assistant / Tool Configuration</span>
            <span class="about-specialism">Addon Design & Data Structuring</span>
          </div>
        </div>

      <section class="panel about-card about-record-card">
        <p class="sheet-label">Core Record</p>

        <div class="about-record-layout">
          <div class="about-portrait-frame">
            <img
              src="/about-portrait-placeholder.png"
              alt="Portrait placeholder for Taylor Heathcote"
            />
          </div>

          <dl class="about-record-list">
            <div>
              <dt>Class</dt>
              <dd>Creative Generalist</dd>
            </div>

            <div>
              <dt>Focus</dt>
              <dd>Game Design / QA / Digital Media</dd>
            </div>

            <div>
              <dt>Region</dt>
              <dd>Nottingham, England</dd>
            </div>

            <div>
              <dt>Status</dt>
              <dd>Open to opportunities</dd>
            </div>

            <div>
              <dt>Education</dt>
              <dd>BSc (Hons) Computer Games Design — First Class</dd>
            </div>
          </dl>
        </div>
      </section>

      <section class="panel about-card about-strengths-card">
        <p class="sheet-label">Strengths</p>

        <div class="strength-list">
          <div class="strength-row">
            <div class="strength-main">
              <h3>Creativity</h3>
              <p>Conceptual thinking, idea generation, and imaginative problem-solving.</p>
            </div>
            <div class="strength-meta">
              <div class="strength-dots" aria-label="Advanced">
                <span class="filled"></span>
                <span class="filled"></span>
                <span class="filled"></span>
                <span class="filled"></span>
                <span class="filled"></span>
              </div>
              <span class="strength-rank">Advanced</span>
            </div>
          </div>

          <div class="strength-row">
            <div class="strength-main">
              <h3>Problem-Solving</h3>
              <p>Refining clarity, structure, usability, and overall cohesion.</p>
            </div>
            <div class="strength-meta">
              <div class="strength-dots" aria-label="Advanced">
                <span class="filled"></span>
                <span class="filled"></span>
                <span class="filled"></span>
                <span class="filled"></span>
                <span class="filled"></span>
              </div>
              <span class="strength-rank">Advanced</span>
            </div>
          </div>

          <div class="strength-row">
            <div class="strength-main">
              <h3>Communication</h3>
              <p>Clear written feedback, documentation, and thoughtful presentation.</p>
            </div>
            <div class="strength-meta">
              <div class="strength-dots" aria-label="Strong">
                <span class="filled"></span>
                <span class="filled"></span>
                <span class="filled"></span>
                <span class="filled"></span>
                <span></span>
              </div>
              <span class="strength-rank">Strong</span>
            </div>
          </div>

          <div class="strength-row">
            <div class="strength-main">
              <h3>Detail Focus</h3>
              <p>Polish, consistency, and how separate parts fit together.</p>
            </div>
            <div class="strength-meta">
              <div class="strength-dots" aria-label="Advanced">
                <span class="filled"></span>
                <span class="filled"></span>
                <span class="filled"></span>
                <span class="filled"></span>
                <span class="filled"></span>
              </div>
              <span class="strength-rank">Advanced</span>
            </div>
          </div>

          <div class="strength-row">
            <div class="strength-main">
              <h3>Adaptability</h3>
              <p>Comfortable learning, iterating, and improving across different tasks.</p>
            </div>
            <div class="strength-meta">
              <div class="strength-dots" aria-label="Strong">
                <span class="filled"></span>
                <span class="filled"></span>
                <span class="filled"></span>
                <span class="filled"></span>
                <span></span>
              </div>
              <span class="strength-rank">Strong</span>
            </div>
          </div>

          <div class="strength-row">
            <div class="strength-main">
              <h3>Collaboration</h3>
              <p>Works well independently and alongside others when building toward a shared goal.</p>
            </div>
            <div class="strength-meta">
              <div class="strength-dots" aria-label="Strong">
                <span class="filled"></span>
                <span class="filled"></span>
                <span class="filled"></span>
                <span class="filled"></span>
                <span></span>
              </div>
              <span class="strength-rank">Strong</span>
            </div>
          </div>
        </div>
      </section>

      <section class="panel about-card about-experience-card">
        <p class="sheet-label">Experience Log</p>

        <div class="experience-entry">
          <h3>Pixel Squad — Video Game QA Tester</h3>
          <p>
            Playtested an early unreleased mobile game build and provided
            detailed feedback on gameplay issues, inconsistencies, and the
            overall player experience.
          </p>
        </div>

        <div class="experience-entry">
          <h3>River Horse Ltd — Board Game QA Tester</h3>
          <p>
            Conducted rigorous playtesting on an unreleased board game,
            identifying gameplay issues and contributing improvement ideas from a
            player-focused perspective.
          </p>
        </div>

        <div class="experience-entry">
          <h3>Browne Jacobson LLP — IT Support</h3>
          <p>
            Supported senior IT staff, handled report-related tasks, and
            contributed early concept thinking toward a website overhaul.
          </p>
        </div>

        <div class="experience-entry">
          <h3>UK Glass Products — Administrative Assistant</h3>
          <p>
            Built organisation, reporting, and coordination skills through
            practical support work in a professional office environment.
          </p>
        </div>
      </section>

      <section class="panel about-card about-proficiencies-card">
        <p class="sheet-label">Proficiencies</p>

        <div class="tool-group">
          <h3>Engines & Interactive Tools</h3>
          <div class="about-chip-list">
            <span class="about-chip">Unreal Engine 4 & 5</span>
            <span class="about-chip">Unity</span>
            <span class="about-chip">UEFN</span>
            <span class="about-chip">Twine</span>
            <span class="about-chip">Valve Hammer Editor</span>
          </div>
        </div>

        <div class="tool-group">
          <h3>Web & Code</h3>
          <div class="about-chip-list">
            <span class="about-chip">Astro</span>
            <span class="about-chip">Java</span>
            <span class="about-chip">C++ (Intermediate)</span>
            <span class="about-chip">C# (Novice)</span>
          </div>
        </div>

        <div class="tool-group">
          <h3>Creative Software</h3>
          <div class="about-chip-list">
            <span class="about-chip">Adobe Creative Suite</span>
            <span class="about-chip">Autodesk Maya</span>
            <span class="about-chip">Blender</span>
          </div>
        </div>

        <div class="tool-group">
          <h3>Workflow & Collaboration</h3>
          <div class="about-chip-list">
            <span class="about-chip">Jira</span>
            <span class="about-chip">GitHub</span>
            <span class="about-chip">Trello</span>
            <span class="about-chip">Notion</span>
            <span class="about-chip">Miro</span>
            <span class="about-chip">Microsoft Office Suite</span>
          </div>
        </div>
      </section>

      <div class="about-side-stack">
        <section class="panel about-card about-education-card">
          <p class="sheet-label">Education</p>

          <div class="education-entry">
            <h3>University of Staffordshire</h3>
            <p>BSc (Honours) Computer Games Design — First Class</p>
            <p class="muted">September 2021 – June 2024</p>
          </div>

          <div class="education-entry">
            <h3>Confetti Institute of Creative Technologies</h3>
            <p>BTEC Level 3 Creative Digital Media — Distinction / Merit / Merit</p>
            <p class="muted">September 2018 – June 2020</p>
          </div>

          <div class="education-entry">
            <h3>Additional Learning</h3>
            <p>Deloitte Data Analytics Job Simulation — Forage</p>
            <p class="muted">December 2025</p>
          </div>
        </section>

        <section class="panel about-card about-focus-card">
          <p class="sheet-label">Current Focus</p>

          <p>
            Right now I’m focused on building a stronger portfolio, refining how I
            present my work, and moving toward early-career opportunities where I
            can contribute through design thinking, QA awareness, communication,
            and thoughtful creative execution.
          </p>

          <ul class="about-focus-list clean-list">
            <li>Building stronger portfolio presentation</li>
            <li>Developing clearer project case studies</li>
            <li>Seeking early-career opportunities in relevant creative roles</li>
          </ul>

          <div class="button-row about-actions">
            <a
              href="/Taylor-Heathcote-CV-2026.pdf"
              class="button button-primary"
              download
            >
              Download Full CV
            </a>
            <a href="/contact" class="button button-secondary">Contact Me</a>
          </div>
        </section>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>
</BaseLayout>